<section id="topLogo">
    <div class="container-fluid heading">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12 text-center p-2">
          <h1>Neighbourhood Library</h1>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12 text-center">
          <img src="/img/ShelfFull.png" width="100%" style="max-width: 400px;">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

</section>


<main>

    <div class="container p-5">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6 pb-4">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-header text-white">
                IT'S ABOUT COMMUNITY
              </div>
              <div class="card-body bg-white">
                <p>A community library lending website serves as an invaluable resource, fostering a sense of shared knowledge and facilitating access to a wide range of books and educational materials.</p>
                     
                <p> Users can login, then make their own books available for lending or check what books their neighbours have to offer. Fostering invaluable knowledge and fellowship with your local neighbours.</p>              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-header text-white">
                IT'S AS EASY AS 1, 2, 3
              </div>
              <div class="card-body bg-white">

                <ul class="heart-list">
                    <li>Register as a participant in your local neighbourhood.</li>
                    <li>Login to see all the awesome books offered by your neighbours.</li>
                    <li>Request a book, or enter titles from your own bookshelf to offer to neighbours.</li>
                  </ul>
             <div class="text-center">
                  <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/login" role="button">register</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>







